    <item>
      <title>罗格夫称拜登和特朗普赞成“炸毁”美国债务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-13/rogoff-says-biden-trump-favor-blowing-up-debt-low-rates-over</link>
      <description><![CDATA[哈佛大学经济学教授肯尼思·罗格夫表示，总统乔·拜登及其前任和挑战者唐纳德·特朗普都有可能将美国债务水平推向危险境地，因为华盛顿未能认识到超低利率时代不会回来。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-13/rogoff-says-biden-trump-favor-blowing-up-debt-low-rates-over</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 17:41:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巴黎俱乐部债权人同意取消索马里 20 亿美元债务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-13/paris-club-creditors-agree-to-cancel-2-billion-of-somali-debt</link>
      <description><![CDATA[世界上最富有的国家同意取消索马里超过20亿美元的债务，以帮助这个饱受战争蹂躏的国家恢复债务可持续性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-13/paris-club-creditors-agree-to-cancel-2-billion-of-somali-debt</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 17:35:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
