    </item>
    <item>
      <title>佐治亚州案件中的特朗普法官驳回了对他的一些指控</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-13/trump-judge-in-georgia-case-dismisses-some-counts-against-him</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普在佐治亚州试图推翻 2020 年总统选举的起诉中取得了部分胜利，法官驳回了针对他和其他被告的几项刑事指控，但庞大的起诉书的大部分内容仍然有效。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-13/trump-judge-in-georgia-case-dismisses-some-counts-against-him</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 14:25:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>苏纳克因种族主义争议拒绝退还捐款</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-13/sunak-refuses-to-return-donation-as-racism-row-embroils-tories</link>
      <description><![CDATA[里希·苏纳克(Rishi Sunak)不顾压力，将一名商人向其保守党退还1000万英镑(1280万美元)的捐款，首相谴责这名商人对反对派政客发表“种族主义”言论。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-13/sunak-refuses-to-return-donation-as-racism-row-embroils-tories</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 12:50:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
